      "raw_text": "A great deal of new work is\nplanned by the Spokane Falls Gas\nLight company for this season.\nMore than 200 men are now en-\ngagged in construction work and\nothers will be put on in the near\nfuture.\n\n\nFifteen carloads of material, val\nued at $4,000, will be here in a few\ndays and will be used in refitting\nthe coal gas generating set Of the\ncompany. II will take about 90\ndays to install the machinery.\nWhen in place it will increase the\ncapacity of the plant one-third."
    }
